{"tid":1747952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政治問題，政治解決呀！","createTime":"2019-11-23T12:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T12:31:49.000Z","uid":298893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"06ab70bc56bb78a2fffdd98ba492d779121c0d2e","tid":1747952,"uid":298893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:29:33.000Z","msg":"好多人仲講話熱狗好唔好投泛民食人血饅頭。。。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌晒你地數簿</span></span><br />\n<br />\n惡法邊個用議會暴力通過㗎？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">邊個搞720集會跟著有721恐襲㗎？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">點解警暴咁嚴重仲有果班契弟話撐警㗎？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲記唔記得盲眼旺死既人班建制點同警暴開脫呀？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解條7婆仲可以居高臨下咁唔當你地係人呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係滿手鮮血既建制派呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n用手上的一票，將賣港賊全部趕走！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日係第1步，無第1步邊有第2步呀！香港人，還拖！"},{"pid":"d0975587e849966a09fe33bd329ccdca7eea7b4a","tid":1747952,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:31:49.000Z","msg":"[深度數據分析] 你知道嗎？多你一票好多<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezEbiS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezEbiS</a>"}]}